      "id": "PopularPost192997",
      "post_content": "Can be a 3 turn drop with haste if you play green and [Fires of Yavimaya](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya)  \n  \nTurn 1: Forest, [Llanowar Elves](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Llanowar Elves)  \nTurn 2: Mountain, [Fires of Yavimaya](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya)  \nTurn 3: Any land, remove [Simian Spirit Guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide) for R, [Savage Firecat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Savage Firecat), swing for 7  \n  \nThe drawback can be huge if you allow the game to drag, so you should work to finish your opponent quickly  \n  \n4/5",
      "posted_by": "Paladin85",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost192997\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Can be a 3 turn drop with haste if you play green and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fires of Yavimaya\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya\">Fires of Yavimaya</a><br/><br/>Turn 1: Forest, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Llanowar Elves\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Llanowar Elves\">Llanowar Elves</a><br/>Turn 2: Mountain, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fires of Yavimaya\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya\">Fires of Yavimaya</a><br/>Turn 3: Any land, remove <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Simian Spirit Guide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide\">Simian Spirit Guide</a> for R, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Savage Firecat\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Savage Firecat\">Savage Firecat</a>, swing for 7<br/><br/>The drawback can be huge if you allow the game to drag, so you should work to finish your opponent quickly<br/><br/>4/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '192997'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy68109\">Paladin85</span>\r\n                                (9/2/2011 5:48:51 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<d