      "post_content": "Here's a great red line-up:\n  \n   \nTurn 1: Drop [Jackal Familiar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jackal Familiar).\n  \nTurn 2: Drop [Mudbrawler Cohort](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mudbrawler Cohort).\n  \nTurn 3: Drop [Aether Membrane](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aether Membrane).\n  \nTurn 4: Drop [Manabarbs](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Manabarbs).\n  \nTurn 5: Drop [Savage Firecat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Savage Firecat).\n  \n   \nSure, you take five damage from playing Savage Firecat, but now you're set for the game! Just don't tap your lands anymore!",
      "posted_by": "Arachibutyrophobia",
